				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13130526/scp-4629#post-4556447</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2020 07:48:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Recette</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1415008</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Funnily enough there's <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5033">another exploding sheep</a> in the contest as well as <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1874">an older one</a>. Of course, the articles are all distinct and have different strengths, but this one makes me imagine the others are just natural mutations and that there'll eventually come a future where the Foundation has enough superpowered sheep to outnumber a superhero league.</p> <p>I'm a big fan of the supernatural phenomenon caused by incredibly specific actions, and this is quite well done.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
